editorialDecl.head: counting of measures
editorialDecl.p: This transcription follows the editorial decisions of the BGA regarding counting of measures.

In the first mdiv "Allegro" measure 6 is directly followed by measure 10 for all parts (containing a fermata) except the piano. The piano part has a cadenza from measure 6 to 9. Measures 7–9 are not written in all other parts except the piano.

Measure 371 and 372 in the first mdiv "Allegro" is divided by a bar line in the piano part. All other parts have one measure 371 where the two measures 371 and 372 in the piano occur. This transcription follows the BGA and adapts to "ignore" the bar line between measure 371 and 372 in the piano.
